### Get all events with filtering
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events
    ?status=open
    &difficulty=easy
    &skip=0
    &limit=10

###

### Get a specific event by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events/1

###

### Create a new event
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Beach Cleanup",
  "description": "Help clean up the local beach and protect marine life",
  "location": "Sunset Beach",
  "date_start": "2024-01-15T09:00:00",
  "date_end": "2024-01-15T12:00:00",
  "difficulty": "medium",
  "duration_minutes": 180,
  "proposed_points": 50,
  "max_participants": 20,
  "organization_id": 1
}

###

### Create another event example
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Food Bank Sorting",
  "description": "Help sort and package food donations for distribution",
  "location": "Central Food Bank, 123 Main St",
  "date_start": "2024-01-20T10:00:00",
  "date_end": "2024-01-20T14:00:00",
  "difficulty": "easy",
  "duration_minutes": 240,
  "proposed_points": 30,
  "max_participants": 15,
  "organization_id": 2
}

###

### Update an existing event
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Beach Cleanup - Extended Hours",
  "description": "Help clean up the local beach with extended hours for more impact",
  "max_participants": 25,
  "proposed_points": 60
}

###

### Update event status
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "closed"
}

###

### Delete an event
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events/1

###

### Close an event (stop accepting applications)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events/1/close

###

### Get upcoming events
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/events/upcoming
    ?limit=5

###

### Get event statistics
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/stats/events

